query:
UPDATE products SET categoryId = (SELECT id FROM categories WHERE slug = 'zodiac-guardians') 
WHERE name LIKE '%Rat Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Ox Guardian Pendant%' 
OR name LIKE '%Tiger Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Rabbit Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Dragon Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Snake Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Horse Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Goat Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Monkey Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Rooster Guardian Pendant%'
OR name LIKE '%Dog Guardian Pendant%' OR name LIKE '%Pig Guardian Pendant%';
